頻道節目





公開方式：公開


**生理學
作者：資訊處

Physiology
生理學
Instructor:
鍾文彬
College of Medicine
Taipei Medical University
Course Structure: 2 Hour per a week

This course that introduces physiological regulation and basic structure of the neuronal, muscular, cardiovascular, digestive, respiratory, urinary, and CNS systems of the human body. The study making classmates systemic reaches the detailed structure and function of the physiological systems and regulation mechanisms. Classmates will benefit by studying this course for their further study on pharmacology, pathology, and clinical applications of the skeleto-muscular system.
本課程主要介紹人體的系統，內容涵蓋神經、肌肉、心臟循環、呼吸、消化、泌尿、內分泌與中樞神經系統之生理學與相關的實驗課程。使同學能夠系統性的學習到人體各系統之間的詳細結構與調控機制。完成本課程的修習，將奠定未來人體各系統的藥理學與病理學的課程。






